In line with the ongoing schemes for Scheduled Tribes by the Tribal Development Department, it has been decided to implement various schemes for the Dhangar community belonging to the Nomadic Tribes-C category in the State vide Notification No. 1 Government Decision referred to herein, d. Taken under 07.08.2019, read under reference No. 2 As per the Government decision, the Government has approved the sanction of long-term loans to the cooperative farmers belonging to the Dhangar community belonging to the Nomadic Tribes-C category in the State.
Accordingly, the government was considering approving the opening of a new head of accounts for the scheme.

Government Decision: - Under the Scheme for Grant of Share Capital to Cooperative Yarn Mills of Dhangar Community of Nomadic Tribes-C Category, long-term loans to Cooperative Yarn Mills of Dhangar Community of Nomadic Tribes-C Category of the State, the following are being approved for opening of accounts for the Scheme: - 2.
